This program is a connect 4 game that implements all the rules of connect 4. 
The user may choose to play against another person or an AI that chooses randomnly.
Incorporating ncurses shows this game in color where the two players are either 
red (X) or one blue (O). Players may choose their own names or the AI's name and face off. 
In the end there's a nice surprise to the winner and a message to the loser hehehe ( •̀ ω •́ )✧.